{"about_the_game":"ENTANGLEMENT is a first person, physics based puzzle platformer that places the player inside a quantum computer. Players will be challenged to master 3 mind bending abilities to solve increasingly difficult puzzles in this indie puzzle game!<br><br>ENTANGLEMENT features 3 unique mechanics that players will use to solve puzzles and reboot the quantum computer!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412970/extras/SizeGif.gif?t=1722211992\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412970/extras/MoveGif.gif?t=1722211992\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412970/extras/SplitGif.gif?t=1722211992\" /><br><br>Size: Grow one Q-bit and shrink the other. Q-bits' voltage change with their size.<br>Move: Q-bits will move in sync with each other. Manipulate 1 Q-bit to indirectly move the other.<br>Split: Split a single Q-bit into 2 smaller Q-bits and subsequently rejoin them at their average position. Alternatively, join 2 Q-bits together into 1 larger Q-bit.<br><br>ENTANGLEMENT is being independently developed by Nth Degree Games.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412970/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1722211992","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412970/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1722211992","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412970/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1722211992","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412970/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1722211992","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"ENTANGLEMENT is a first person, physics based